This project implements UI generation for Xamarin Forms (Android and iOS) for the OKHOSTING.UI framework

	  Open source multi-platform UI framework. Create your apps once on PCL and have your UI generated on runtime for ASP.NET, Windows Forms, WPF, Linux (Mono + WinForms), Mac OS (Mono + WinForms and Xamarin.Mac), iOS, Android, Windows Phone (via Xamarin.Forms) and Windows Universal Platform.

	  ## Features

	  * Create your apps in PCL and run them everywhere, truly multi-platform (web included)
	  * The UI is defined from code (XAML designer on the way)
	  * 100% native controls are used in all platforms
	  * You have only the "common" UI api surface among all platforms
	  * Supports click, doble click and, for user input controls, value changed events
	  * Using OKHOSTING.UI.CSS you can use CSS files to define the styles of your controls on all platforms (thanks to AngleSharp)

	  ## Supported controls

	  * Autocomplete
	  * Button
	  * Calendar
	  * CheckBox
	  * HyperLink
	  * Image
	  * Label
	  * ListPicker (equivalent to a DropDownList)
	  * PasswordTextBox
	  * TextArea
	  * TextBox

	  Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.UI

BugBot is a debugger robot, based on the windbg APIs. It can support remote, kernel, or local debugging.
      The robot is designed to be initialized once, with interface classes providing the needed output and trigger functionality.
      It's intended to make collecting hard to reproduce crash dumps easier, but it can also record standard debug output from a running process or kernel.

BugBot is a debugger robot, based on the windbg APIs. It can support remote, kernel, or local debugging.
      The robot is designed to be initialized once, with interface classes providing the needed output and trigger functionality.
      It's intended to make collecting hard to reproduce crash dumps easier, but it can also record standard debug output from a running process or kernel.

This project implements UI generation for the Universal Windows Platform under the OKHOSTING.UI framework

	  Open source multi-platform UI framework. Create your apps once on PCL and have your UI generated on runtime for ASP.NET, Windows Forms, WPF, Linux (Mono + WinForms), Mac OS (Mono + WinForms and Xamarin.Mac), iOS, Android, Windows Phone (via Xamarin.Forms) and Windows Universal Platform.

	  ## Features

	  * Create your apps in PCL and run them everywhere, truly multi-platform (web included)
	  * The UI is defined from code (XAML designer on the way)
	  * 100% native controls are used in all platforms
	  * You have only the "common" UI api surface among all platforms
	  * Supports click, doble click and, for user input controls, value changed events
	  * Using OKHOSTING.UI.CSS you can use CSS files to define the styles of your controls on all platforms (thanks to AngleSharp)

	  ## Supported controls

	  * Autocomplete
	  * Button
	  * Calendar
	  * CheckBox
	  * HyperLink
	  * Image
	  * Label
	  * ListPicker (equivalent to a DropDownList)
	  * PasswordTextBox
	  * TextArea
	  * TextBox

	  Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.UI

This project implements UI generation for Windows Presentation Foundation for the OKHOSTING.UI framework

	  Open source multi-platform UI framework. Create your apps once on PCL and have your UI generated on runtime for ASP.NET, Windows Forms, WPF, Linux (Mono + WinForms), Mac OS (Mono + WinForms and Xamarin.Mac), iOS, Android, Windows Phone (via Xamarin.Forms) and Windows Universal Platform.

	  ## Features

	  * Create your apps in PCL and run them everywhere, truly multi-platform (web included)
	  * The UI is defined from code (XAML designer on the way)
	  * 100% native controls are used in all platforms
	  * You have only the "common" UI api surface among all platforms
	  * Supports click, doble click and, for user input controls, value changed events
	  * Using OKHOSTING.UI.CSS you can use CSS files to define the styles of your controls on all platforms (thanks to AngleSharp)

	  ## Supported controls

	  * Autocomplete
	  * Button
	  * Calendar
	  * CheckBox
	  * HyperLink
	  * Image
	  * Label
	  * ListPicker (equivalent to a DropDownList)
	  * PasswordTextBox
	  * TextArea
	  * TextBox

	  Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.UI

Cng based crypto library to help with securing web endpoints and data at rest:
      - create/export/import ECDSA (P521, P384, P256) certificates
      - RSA, AES
      - JWT using ECDSA signing
      - Encrypt/Decrypt data using AES, assuming AES key is encrypted using RSA certificate
      - Stream based
      
      Initially created to work with the Kalix 'Leo' engine (see Kalix.Leo)
summary: Library to help secure web endpoints and data at rest. Uses ECDSA (P521, P384, P256) to create tokens using JWT. Encrypt/Decrypt data using AES, assuming AES key is encrypted using RSA certificate.

This project implements UI generation for ASP.NET Web Forms for the OKHOSTING.UI framework

	  Open source multi-platform UI framework. Create your apps once on PCL and have your UI generated on runtime for ASP.NET, Windows Forms, WPF, Linux (Mono + WinForms), Mac OS (Mono + WinForms and Xamarin.Mac), iOS, Android, Windows Phone (via Xamarin.Forms) and Windows Universal Platform.

	  ## Features

	  * Create your apps in PCL and run them everywhere, truly multi-platform (web included)
	  * The UI is defined from code (XAML designer on the way)
	  * 100% native controls are used in all platforms
	  * You have only the "common" UI api surface among all platforms
	  * Supports click, doble click and, for user input controls, value changed events
	  * Using OKHOSTING.UI.CSS you can use CSS files to define the styles of your controls on all platforms (thanks to AngleSharp)

	  ## Supported controls

	  * Autocomplete
	  * Button
	  * Calendar
	  * CheckBox
	  * HyperLink
	  * Image
	  * Label
	  * ListPicker (equivalent to a DropDownList)
	  * PasswordTextBox
	  * TextArea
	  * TextBox

	  Please visit: https://github.com/okhosting/OKHOSTING.UI
summary: Open source multi-platform UI framework. Create your apps once on PCL and have your UI generated on runtime for ASP.NET, Windows Forms, WPF, Linux (Mono + WinForms), Mac OS (Mono + WinForms and Xamarin.Mac), iOS, Android, Windows Phone (via Xamarin.Forms) and Windows Universal Platform.
